parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the power steering system can cause the steering wheel to become difficult to turn, making it hard to control the vehicle, which can lead to accidents or loss of control, especially at high speeds.
symptoms: The power steering assist fails
the steering wheel becomes stiff or difficult to turn
the "Service Power Steering" warning light is illuminated
the stabili-trak warning light is illuminated
the vehicle loses motive power
the power steering fails intermittently
the vehicle requires excessive force to steer.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the steering gearbox can cause the power steering system to fail, leading to a loss of control and increasing the risk of accidents.
symptoms: The steering gearbox needs to be replaced
the power steering gear fails
the steering column needs to be replaced.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the electrical power steering assist can cause the power steering system to fail, leading to a loss of control and increasing the risk of accidents.
symptoms: The electrical power steering assist fails
the power steering assist and stabili-trak warning lights are illuminated
the vehicle loses power steering functionality.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The transmission shifting issues can cause hesitation, jerking, or lurching of the vehicle, leading to accidents or loss of control, especially in heavy traffic or when merging onto highways.
symptoms: Hesitation or delay in shifting
jerking or lurching of the vehicle
failure to downshift
rough shifting
and unpredictable transmission behavior.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The 4-wheel drive transfer case issues can cause the vehicle to become stuck in 4-wheel drive mode, leading to loss of control, accidents, or being stranded.
symptoms: Vehicle stuck in 4-wheel drive mode
unable to switch out of 4-wheel drive
service 4-wheel drive warning light illuminated
and corrosion in the range selector connectors.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The ignition locking solenoid failure can cause the key to become stuck in the ignition, making it difficult or impossible to leave the vehicle unattended, leading to theft or battery failure.
symptoms: Key stuck in the ignition
unable to remove the key from the ignition.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the power steering control gearbox can cause the vehicle to lose power steering, resulting in difficulty steering the vehicle, which can lead to accidents or loss of control.
symptoms: The vehicle loses power steering
the stability light comes on
the vehicle slows down on its own
and the service lights come on on the dashboard.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the touch screen display can cause distractions while driving, leading to accidents or loss of control.
symptoms: The touch screen display becomes erratic or unresponsive
buttons click on their own
the display changes or radio stations change
and the screen is unresponsive to input.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the clutch and transmission can cause the vehicle to lose power, resulting in difficulty shifting gears, which can lead to accidents or loss of control.
symptoms: The clutch pedal feels soft or spongy
the clutch pedal sticks to the floor
the clutch pedal does not return to its normal position
and the vehicle is unable to shift into gear.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the electrical system can cause various systems to malfunction, leading to accidents or loss of control.
symptoms: The instrument panel lights turn off intermittently
the dashboard information lights turn off
and the backup camera display dims or becomes difficult to see.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the brake system can cause the vehicle to lose braking ability, leading to accidents or loss of control.
symptoms: The vehicle's anti-lock braking system and stability control system malfunction
and the brake assist system fails.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the key and ignition system can cause the vehicle to become stuck in gear or unable to start, leading to inconvenience and potential safety risks.
symptoms: The key cannot be removed from the ignition
and the vehicle is stuck in gear.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the defroster and heater system can cause reduced visibility while driving, leading to accidents or loss of control.
symptoms: The rear defroster emits smoke
overheats
and cracks the rear windshield
and the heater and defroster system fails to work properly.
